<title>yạ rby yạ sẖms sạṭʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bḥbk yạrby lyh? ạkyd ʿsẖạn fdytny
 wlạ lmạ knt ḍạyʿ lqytny
 wjyt ndytny
 ạlqrạr- yạrby yạ sẖms sạṭʿ bnwr wbhạʾ rạỷʿ
 ạsẖrq ʿlyạ bnwrk bjlạl wmjd ṭạlʿ
 2- bḥbk yạrby lyh? ʿlsẖạn sạtr ʿly
 wlmạ bạrjʿlk tạyb btfrḥ ạlsmạ by
 3- bḥbk yạrby lyh? lạnk sr njạḥy bdwnk mạ ạswy sẖyʾ wbfyḍ nʿmk tmlạny</lyrics>
</song>